This test code contains a main driver which executes either a C OpenMP kernel, or three different kernels ( C OpenMP, FORTRAN OpenMP, CUDA FORTRAN ).

Cuda-memcheck is able to spot the illegal write operation in the CUDA kernel, but fails to report it for the OpenMP kernel versions.

XLF CUDAFORTRAN
XLC OPENMP4.5 C
XLF OPENMP4.5 FORTRAN

-- Aaron Black
black27@llnl.gov
